                        <div class="about-content">
                          <h1 class="fs-4 fw-bold mb-3">About Us</h1>
                          
                          <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-3">Start Playing Merge Rot Today!</h2>
                          <p>Welcome to <strong>Merge Rot</strong>, the browser-based puzzle game that combines addictive merge mechanics with the fun of internet meme culture. In this engaging game, you will drop quirky items and characters into a container, where they collide and merge into larger and more bizarre forms.</p>
                          
                          <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-3">Strategic Gameplay</h2>
                          <p>In <strong>Merge Rot</strong>, players must think strategically and be aware of their surroundings. You'll need to make quick decisions to prevent the container from overflowing while maximizing your merging potential. This blend of strategy and fast-paced gameplay ensures that every session remains exciting and unpredictable.</p>
                          
                          <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-3">Vibrant Visuals and Themes</h2>
                          <p>The game features vibrant, meme-inspired visuals that capture the essence of various themes, including Italian Brainrot, Dogs, Cats, Fellas, Capybaras, and Giga. Each theme brings its own unique charm and adds to the chaotic atmosphere of the game.</p>
                          
                          <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-3">Accessible and Replayable</h2>
                          <p>With intuitive drag-and-drop controls, <strong>Merge Rot</strong> is easy to pick up and play. The physics-based gameplay allows for creative experimentation without the pressure of strict win/loss conditions. This makes it a stress-free and endlessly replayable sandbox experience.</p>
                          
                          <h2 class="fs-5 fw-bold mb-3">Join the Fun</h2>
                          <p>Ready to experience the chaos and creativity of <strong>Merge Rot</strong>? Start playing now and immerse yourself in a world of bizarre merges and endless fun! For support, contact us at <a href="mailto:support@mergerot.co">support@mergerot.co</a>.</p>
                        </div>
                    </article>
                </div>
